dct_title_s: Map of the United States / by J.H. Young ; engraved by J.H. Young, D. Haines & F. Dankworth.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Prime meridian: Washington. Includes inset "Map of North America, including all the recent geographical discoveries," 8 urban area insets, text, distance table for the Erie and Champlain canals, diagrams of heights of mountains and lengths of rivers, statistical tables, and ill. 1836
